n%20border%20points%20connecting%20Delhi%20with%20its%20satellite%20towns%20led%20to%20a%20traffic%20nightmare%20yesterday.%20Commuters%2C%20mostly%20office%20goers%2C%20were%20stuck%20for%20hours%20at%20different%20city%20border%20points%20due%20to%20a%20crawling%20traffic.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707885780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbv929608_farmers-protest-pti_625x300_14_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-farmers-march-to-delhi-protesting-farmers-to-resume-delhi-march-after-night-halt-10-points-5053872%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Protesting%20farmers%20will%20soon%20resume%20their%20march%20towards%20Delhi%20after%20a%20night%20halt.%20A%20fresh%20attempt%20will%20be%20made%20to%20push%20forward%20against%20a%20huge%20security%20deployment%20to%20reach%20the%20capital%20with%20a%20list%20of%20their%20key%20demands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-farmers-march-to-delhi-protesting-farmers-to-resume-delhi-march-after-night-halt-10-points-5053872%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Photos%3A%20Delhi's%20Singhu%20Border%20Is%20a%20Maze%20of%20Barricades%20as%20Govt%20Works%20to%20Keep%20Farmers%20Away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14095218%2FIMG-20240213-WA0043.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%2C%20where%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20are%20approaching%20in%20protest%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20deployed%20significant%20security%20forces.%20There%20are%20battalions%20of%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20(RAF)%2C%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20guard%20the%20Singhu%20border%20and%20prevent%20farmers%E2%80%99%20entry%20into%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E