ts%20have%20suggested%20is%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan's%20lack%20of%20game-time%20after%20the%20Tour%20ended%20may%20have%20raised%20a%20few%20eyebrows.%20Despite%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20needs%20to%20play%20some%20form%20of%20cricket%2C%20to%20make%20a%20national%20team%20comeback%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20been%20absent%20from%20the%20scene.%20Despite%20the%20ongoing%20Ranji%20Trophy%20campaign%2C%20Ishan%20has%20not%20been%20competing%20in%20the%20premier%20domestic%20competition%20and%20rather%20training%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20have%20led%20to%20speculation%20about%20Ishan%20Kishan's%20future%20in%20Indian%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Kishan%20Kishan%20would%20find%20himself%20out%20of%20BCCI%20retainership%20(he%20has%20a%20grade%20C%20annual%20contract%20of%20Rs%201%20crore)%2C%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20official%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20discussions%20have%20taken%20place%20as%20of%20now%20regarding%20central%20contracts.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Americas%2C%20starting%20from%20June%201%20and%20India%20playing%20their%20opening%20game%20on%20June%205%20in%20New%20York%2C%20the%20workload%20of%20India's%20core%20group%20of%20players%20during%20the%20IPL%2C%20which%20is%20going%20to%20be%20tentatively%20scheduled%20between%20March%2022%20to%20May%2026%2C%20will%20be%20very%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20no%20Indian%20players%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20given%20any%20instructions%20about%20workload%20management%20during%20IPL%20as%20it%20is%20also%20not%20fair%20to%20the%20franchises%2C%20who%20are%20paying%20top%20dollar%20to%20star%20Indian%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%