didate%2C%20and%20David%20Sacks%2C%20a%20co-founder%20of%20Craft%20Ventures%20LLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20comments%20came%20as%20he%20agreed%20with%20Johnson's%20statement%20that%20Putin%20would%20not%20lose%20in%20Ukraine.%20Johnson%20said%20those%20who%20expect%20a%20Ukraine%20victory%20were%20%26quot%3Bliving%20in%20a%20fantasy%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20gotta%20kill%20this%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said%20of%20the%20%2495%20billion%20measure%2C%20which%20includes%20%2460%20billion%20in%20assistance%20for%20Ukraine%20as%20well%20as%20funding%20for%20Israel%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20and%20humanitarian%20aid%20for%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20added%20he%20hoped%20Americans%20would%20contact%20their%20elected%20representatives%20about%20the%20Ukraine%20bill.%20%26quot%3BThis%20spending%20does%20not%20help%20Ukraine.%20Prolonging%20the%20war%20does%20not%20help%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20expressed%20similar%20sentiments%20before%20on%20X%2C%20doubting%20Ukraine's%20ability%20to%20win%20the%20war%20and%20mocking%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy's%20requests%20for%20aid.%20The%20tech%20mogul%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20from%20Ukraine%20and%20Democratic%20members%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20there%20was%20pressure%20on%20Putin%20to%20see%20the%20fight%20through.%20%26quot%3BIf%20he%20were%20to%20back%20off%2C%20he%20would%20be%20assassinated%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20told%20the%20senators%20he's%20sometimes%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20Putin%20apologist%2C%20but%20said%20that%20accusation%20was%20%26quot%3Babsurd.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20his%20companies%20%26quot%3Bhave%20probably%20done%20more%20to%20undermine%20Russia%20than%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20SpaceX%20providing%20Starlink%20internet%20service%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20has%20been%20critical%20to%20the%20nation's%20communications%20after%20Russia%20invaded%2C%20as%20well%20as%20SpaceX%20taking%20business%20away%20from%20Russia's%20space%20launch%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20views%20contrast%20strongly%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Senate%20Republican%20leader%20Mitch%20McConnell%2C%20who%20argue%20that%20aiding%20Ukraine's%20defense%20against%20the%20Kremlin%20is%20in%20America's%20interests%20and%20will%20help%20deter%20other%20autocrats%20from%20starting%20wars%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Senate%20continued%20work%20on%20the%20bill%20late%20Monday%20night%2C%20and%20it%20was%20expected%20to%20pass%2C%20but%20House%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20has%20insisted%20border%20security%20measures%20must%20come%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20his%20interest%20is%20in%20stopping%20the%20deaths%20of%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20war%2C%20adding%20he%20doubted%20the%20wisdom%20of%20seeking%20Putin's%20ouster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20who%20want%20regime%20change%20in%20Russia%2C%20they%20should%20think%20about%20who%20is%20the%20person%20that%20could%20take%20out%20Putin%2C%20and%20is%20that%20person%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20peacenik%3F%20Probably%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20such%20a%20person%20would%20likely%20be%20%26quot%3Beven%20more%20hardcore%20than%20Putin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707876660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ffrr9q5p_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_02_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvladimir-putin-would-be-assassinated-if-he-backs-out-of-ukraine-elon-musk-5053869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20told%20US%20Republican%20senators%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20way%20in%20hell%26quot%3B%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vla