0they%20had%20to%20make%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20device%20%E2%80%94%20in%20comfort%20and%20ergonomics%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20display%20and%20artifacts%20to%20get%20to%20that%20%5Bhigher%20resolution%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Zuckerberg%20seemed%20to%20relish%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20Apple%20couldn't%20do%20everything%20well.%20At%20least%20not%20on%20the%20first%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20look%20around%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20just%20assumed%20that%20Vision%20Pro%20would%20be%20higher%20quality%20because%20it's%20Apple%20and%20it%20costs%20%243%2C000%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20honestly%2C%20I'm%20pretty%20surprised%20that%20Quest%20is%20so%20much%20better%20for%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20things%20that%20people%20use%20these%20headsets%20for%20with%20that%20price%20differential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFanboy%20takedown%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20Meta%20CEO%20did%20the%20unforgivable.%20He%20mocked%20Apple's%20legion%20of%20adoring%20fans.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20some%20fanboys%20get%20upset%20whenever%20anyone%20dares%20to%20question%20if%20Apple's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20leader%20in%20a%20new%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20every%20generation%20of%20computing%20has%20an%20open%20and%20a%20closed%20model.%20And%20yeah%2C%20in%20mobile%2C%20Apple's%20closed%20model%20won%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20always%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20went%20on%20to%20position%20Meta%20as%20being%20on%20track%20to%20win%20against%20Apple%20in%20at%20least%20the%20mixed%20reality%20headset%20race%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20back%20to%20the%20PC%20era%2C%20Microsoft's%20open%20model%20was%20the%20winner%2C%20and%20in%20this%20next%20generation%20Meta%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20open%20model.%20And%20I%20really%20wa