%20trial.%20Some%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20Democrats%2C%20who%20hold%20a%20narrow%20majority%2C%20could%20avoid%20a%20trial%20altogether.%20There%20could%20also%20be%20an%20early%20move%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20impeachment%20provides%20another%20avenue%20for%20the%20GOP%20to%20hammer%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20over%20immigration.%20Polls%20show%20that%20the%20American%20people%20are%20deeply%20unhappy%20with%20the%20current%20crisis%20at%20the%20U.S.%20Southern%20border.%20Biden%20has%20emphasized%20how%20the%20White%20House%20tried%20to%20strike%20a%20bipartisan%20border-Ukraine%20deal%20only%20for%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20House%20Republicans%20to%20nuke%20the%20agreement%20shortly%20after%20its%20public%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fmtg-alejandro-mayorkas-impeachment-trial-house-managers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20moment%20for%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Georgia%20Republican%20was%20booted%20from%20her%20committee%20assignments%20shortly%20after%20she%20arrived%20in%20Washington.%20She%20quickly%20became%20then-House%20Minority%20Leader%20Kevin%20McCarthy's%20ally%2C%20which%20paid%20dividends%20during%20his%20brief%20speakership.%20Greene%2C%20who%20wrote%20the%20initial%20impeachment%20articles%20against%20Mayorkas%2C%20is%20set%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20House%20manager%2C%20a%20group%20of%20members%20that%20formally%20presents%20their%20case%20to%20the%20Senate.%20Past%20House%20managers%20have%20included%20Sen.%20Lindsey%20Graham%20and%20Rep.%20Adam%20Schiff%2C%20a%20California%20Democrat%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20gained%20a%20larger%20national%20profile%20after%20serving%20as%20managers%20during%20impeachment%20trials%20against%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20Trump%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%2