e%20in%20Basirhat%20after%20being%20stopped%20from%20holding%20a%20protest.%20The%20police%20said%20the%20protesters%20threw%20stones%20at%20them%20and%20there%20is%20video%20footage%20to%20identify%20those%20involved.%20Several%20policemen%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Majumdar%20had%20taken%20a%20local%20train%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20anticipating%20police%20blockades%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20reaching%20Basirhat%2C%20an%20area%20in%20the%20same%20north%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20where%20prohibitory%20orders%20banning%20large%20gatherings%20is%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20police%20lathicharged%20the%20protesters%20and%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells%20to%20disperse%20them%2C%20they%20retaliated%20with%20stones.%20The%20clash%20took%20place%20outside%20the%20office%20of%20the%20local%20Superintendent%20of%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukanta%20Majumdar%20claimed%20it%20was%20the%20police%20who%20used%20batons%20first%2C%20without%20provocation.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20the%20police%20launched%20a%20lathicharge%2C%20it%20then%20pelted%20stones%20and%20later%20tear%20gas%20shells%20were%20used%20on%20our%20workers.%20Then%2C%20our%20workers%20were%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnTrinamool%20workers%20have%20been%20raping%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20for%20years%20now%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20naming%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20Shibu%20Hajra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar%20in%20this%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20come%20to%20the%20SP%20with%20the%20demand%20to%20arrest%20them...%20We%20also%20demand%20that%20our%20arrested%20workers%20will%20have%20to%20be%20released.%20If%20this%20is%20not%20done%2C%20we%20will%20sit%20here%20all%20through%20the%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20starting%20a%20sit-in%20protest%20at%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20Sumit%20Kumar%20said%20there%20was%20stone%20pelting%20and%20they%20used%20