umbers%20recently%20listed%20by%20the%20UK%20and%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68289482%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68289482.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68289482.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20UAE%20Sign%20Bilateral%20Investment%20Treaty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14003458%2FModi-and-Sheikh.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20seventh%20visit%20to%20the%20Gulf%20kingdom%2C%20India%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20signed%20eight%20pacts%2C%20including%20a%20bilateral%20investment%20treaty%20and%20a%20framework%20deal%20to%20foster%20regional%20connectivity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20first%20leg%20of%20his%20foreign%20tour%2C%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2013)%2C%20his%20seventh%20visit%20and%20the%20third%20time%20that%20he%20was%20in%20the%20UAE%20in%20the%20last%20one%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20greeted%20by%20the%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20President%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20following%20which%20they%20held%20delegation-level%20talks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20Modi%20addressed%20an%20Indian%20community%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20readout%20issued%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20witnessed%20the%20signing%20of%20eight%20agreements%2C%20with%20the%20first%20one%20being%20a%20bilateral%20investment%20treaty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20agreement%20will%20be%20a%20key%20enabler%20for%20further%20promoting%20investments%20in%20both%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20statement%20from%20the%20Indian%20side.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20fourth-largest%20foreign%20investor%20is%20the%20UAE%20and%20discussions%20regarding%20the%20investment%20treaty%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20been%20ongoing%20since%202016.%20One%20of%20the%20final%20aspects%20to%20be%20settled%20was%20the%20arbitration%20clause.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20this%20treaty%2C%20disputing%20parties%20will%20have%20a%20four-year%20window%20to%20resolve%20their%20issues%20before%20resorting%20to%20arbitration%2C%20as%20per%20sources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20May%202022%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20with%20the%20UAE%20came%20into%20force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20bilateral%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20stands%20at%20%2485%20million.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20sides%20also%20signed%20an%20%E2%80%9CIntergovernmental%20Framework%20Agreement%20between%20India%20and%20UAE%20on%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20the%20MEA%2C%20would%20foster%20cooperation%20furthering%20regional%20connectivity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20they%20also%20signed%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20on%20electrical%20interconnection%20and%20trade%2C%20which%20was%20to%20strengthen%20energy%20security%2C%20as%20per%20the%20MEA%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20readout%20noted%20that%20during%20their%20talks%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20their%20energy%20partnership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20recognising%20the%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20as%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20providers%20of%20crude%20oil%20and%20liquefied%20petroleum%20gas%20to%20India%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20also%20highlighted%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%20engagement%20in%20long-term%20agreements%20for%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%2C%20said%20the%20MEA%E2%80%99s%20press%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20five%20agreements%20were%20inked%2C%20covering%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20financial%20payments%2C%20archives%20and%20heritage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%20visit%2C%20RITES%20Limited%20and%20the%20Gujarat%20Maritime%20Board%20signed%20agreements%20with%20the%20Abu%20Dhabi%20Ports%20Company%20related%20to%20port%20infrastructure%20and%20connectivity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20Indian%20community%20event%20termed%20%E2%80%98Ahlan%20Modi%E2%80%99%20on%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20and%20%5Bthe%5D%20UAE%20are%20partners%20in%20progress.%20Our%20relationship%20is%20of%20talent%2C%20innovation%20and%20culture%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20partnership%20is%20getting%20stronger%20in%20all%20areas%20and%20reaching%20newer%20heights.%20It%E2%80%99s%20India%E2%80%99s%20wish%20that%20our%20partnership%20keeps%20getting%20strong%20every%20passing%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20also%20thanked%20the%20UAE%20president%20for%20conferring%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20highest%20civilian%20award%2C%20the%20Order%20of%20Zayed%2C%20upon%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%2C%20he%20will%20be%20inaugurating%20the%20BAPS%20Hindu%20temple%2C%20which%20has%20apparently%20been%20constructed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20%2416%20million.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20their%20meeting%2C%20Modi%20appreciated%20the%20UAE%20president%20for%20granting%20land%