0are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-farmers-head-to-delhi-for-protest-haryana-govt-creates-hurdles-on-their-path%5C%22%3Ecurrently%20marching%20to%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20demanding%20assured%20prices%20for%20their%20crops%20and%20debt%20waivers%20(among%20other%20things)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fprominent-farmers-body-skm-which-spearheaded-2020-21-stir-yet-to-take-call-on-joining-delhi-chalo%2F1964934%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20SKM%20is%20reportedly%20undecided%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20whether%20to%20formally%20join%20the%20latest%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%2C%20however%2C%20echoed%20the%20demands%20of%20groups%20that%20are%20on%20their%20way%20to%20Delhi%20and%20have%20decried%20the%20police%20action%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20observe%20with%20deep%20regret%20that%20instead%20of%20solving%20these%20problems%2C%20your%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20form%20and%20conduct%20the%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20all%20these%20issues%20and%20resolve%20them%20in%20a%20time%20bound%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SKM%20said%20in%20its%20letter%20to%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20it%20repealed%20the%20controversial%20farm%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20the%20enactment%20of%20which%20was%20the%20major%20trigger%20for%20the%20past%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20%E2%80%93%20in%202021%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Fwhy-indian-farmers-are-marching-protest-capital-2024-02-13%2F%5C%22%3Epromised%20to%20form%20a%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20farmers%20and%20officials%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20ensure%20minimum%20support%20prices%20for%20all%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20letter%20also%20blamed%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20being%20hesitant%20to%20engage%20in%20talks%20with%20it%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Union%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20governments%20%E2%80%93%20all%20controlled%20by%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinflict%5Bing%5D%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20terror%20on%20common%20farmers%E2%80%9D%20by%20%E2%80%9Cresort%5Bing%5D%20to%20repressive%20measures%20on%20peaceful%20protests%20%5Bby%5D%20farmers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20make%20clear%20that%20all%20these%20three%20measures%20are%20unacceptable%20in%20responsible%20governance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20protest%20the%20repression%20unleashed%20on%20farmers%20today%20at%20%5Bthe%5D%20Punjab%20border%20%5Bby%5D%20unleashing%20%3Cem%3Elathi%3C%2Fem%3E%20charge%2C%20rubber%20bullet%20and%20tear%20gas%20shelling%2C%20making%20many%20injured%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SKM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20Haryana%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpolice-use-tear-gas-on-protesting-farmers-at-punjab-haryana-border%5C%22%3Efired%20tear%20gas%20at%20protesting%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20police%20action%2C%20the%20SKM%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20in%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunited%20and%20single%20minded%20and%20will%20resist%20any%20such%20act%20of%20authoritarianism%20and%20excessive%20use%20of%20state%20power%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20demands%20the%20SKM%20brought%20up%20were%20to%20not%20raise%20the%20electricity%20tariff%2C%20300%20units%E2%80%99%20worth%20free%20electricity%20supply%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfarming%20and%20for%20domestic%20use%20and%20shops%E2%80%9D%2C%20crop%20insurance%20payable%20for%20damage%20to%20each%20plot%20of%20land%20and%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20hike%20in%20monthly%20pensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20referred%20to%20a%20demand%20to%20prosecute%20and%20incarcerate%20BJP%20MP%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%2C%20who%20some%20farmers%20have%20accused%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ffarmers-workers-to-mark-black-day-on-tuesday-to-seek-ajay-mishra-tenis-dismissal-over-lakhimpur-kheri-killings-2709235%5C%22%3Ebeing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchief%20conspirator%E2%80%9D%20behind%20an%20incident%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20his%20son%20and%20others%20allegedly%20mowed%20to%20death%20four%20farmers%20protesting%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20we%20urge%20you%20to%20take%20sympathy%20on%20the%20plight%20of%20farmers%20in%20the%20face%20of%20severe%20onslaught%20of%20the%20corporate%20intervention%20in%20agriculture%20actively%20supported%20by%20the%20Union%20Budgets%20and%20departmental%20actions%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20concluded%20its%20letter%20by%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20full%20letter%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha-%20(SKM)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13th%20February%202024%2C%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetter%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnNarendra%20Modi%20ji%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnHon%E2%80%99ble%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%3Cbr%3E%5CnNorth%20Block%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Govt%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubject%3A%20Failure%20to%20Fulfill%20Promises%20to%20Farmers%20and%20Repression%20Let%20Loose%20on%20Farmers%20Protest%20in%20Punjab%20%E2%80%93%20Haryana%20Border.%20Kisan%20Movement%20will%20resist%20united%20and%20single%20minded%20any%20act%20of%20authoritarianism%20and%20excessive%20use%20of%20state%20power%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESir%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20write%20to%20you%20once%20again%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20our%20All%20India%20call%20for%20an%20Industrial%20%2F%20Sectoral%20Strike%20and%20Grameen%20Bharat%20Bandh%20on%20February%2016%2C%202024%20in%20support%20of%20the%2021%20point%20demand%20charter%20of%20farmers%20and%20workers%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20your%20government%20will%20see%20reason%20to%20address%20and%20solve%20the%20problems%20you%20had%20promised%20to%20SKM%20on%20Dec%209%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20reminder%20we%20are%20briefing%20for%20your%20reference%20on%20these%20issues.%20They%20are%20MSP%20for%20all%20crops%20at%20Swaminathan%20formula%20of%20C2%2B50%25%20with%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20procurement%3B%20debt%20waiver%20with%20reduction%20in%20input%20costs%3B%20no%20raise%20in%20electricity%20tariff%20and%20no%20to%20smart%20metres%20as%20per%20the%20new%20electricity%20bill%3B%20free%20300%20units%20electricity%20for%20farming%20and%20for%20domestic%20use%20and%20shops%3B%20comprehensive%20crop%20insurance%20payable%20for%20damage%20to%20each%20plot%20of%20land%3B%20punishment%20to%20Guilty%20of%20Lakhimpur%20carnage%20including%20sending%20main%20accused%20Ajay%20Misra%20Teni%20to%20jail%3B%20hike%20in%20pensions%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20observe%20with%20deep%20regret%20that%20in%20place%20of%20solving%20these%20problems%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA.%20Your%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20form%20and%20conduct%20the%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20all%20these%20issues%20and%20resolve%20them%20in%20a%20time%20bound%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EB.%20Your%20ministers%20have%20been%20hesitant%20to%20talk%20with%20SKM%20while%20more%20interested%20to%20talk%20with%20other%20platforms%20to%20project%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20is%20divided%20in%20order%20to%20escape%20from%20your%20constitutional%20responsibility%20of%20solving%20the%20problems%20that%20distress%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EC.%20Your%20govt%20and%20that%20of%20Haryana%20and%20UP%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20have%20resorted%20to%20repressive%20measures%20on%20peaceful%20protests%20of%20farmers%20and%20inflict%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20terror%20on%20common%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20would%20like%20to%20make%20clear%20that%20all%20these%20three%20measures%20are%20unacceptable%20in%20responsible%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20strongly%20protest%20the%20