1597_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20AAP%20Throws%20Down%20Gauntlet%20With%20One-Seat%20Offer%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Congress%20%E2%80%98Energised%E2%80%99%20to%20Fight%20All%207%20Seats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13212259%2FAAP-n-Cong.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20With%20no%20final%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20in%20sight%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20has%20thrown%20the%20gauntlet%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20Delhi%20and%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20offer%20one%20seat%20though%20it%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cdeserve%20a%20single%20seat%20on%20merit%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cenergised%E2%80%9D%20to%20fight%20on%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20offer%20comes%20just%20days%20after%20the%20AAP%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20go%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-aap-to-go-solo-in-punjab-major-setback-for-india%2Farticleshow%2F107580814.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esolo%20and%20fight%20on%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20political%20affairs%20committee%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2013)%2C%20AAP%20MP%20and%20national%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20said%20that%20its%20one-seat%20offer%20to%20the%20Congress%20comes%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20%E2%80%9Calliance%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edharma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20two%20official%20meetings%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20on%20January%208%20and%20January%2012.%20The%20talks%20happened%20in%20a%20good%20atmosphere%20on%20all%20issues%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20results.%20After%20these%20two%20official%20meetings%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20meeting%20in%20the%20last%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pathak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20a%20month%20waiting%20for%20the%20next%20meeting%20which%20would%20take%20talks%20forward.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20%5BBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%5D%20Yatra%20is%20going%20on%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20delay.%20We%20kept%20waiting%20and%20we%20met%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20during%20this%2C%20but%20even%20they%20had%20no%20idea%2C%20no%20clarity%20about%20the%20next%20meeting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20these%20circumstances%2C%20if%20your%20objective%20is%20to%20win%20elections%2C%20it%20will%20become%20very%20difficult%20to%20do%20so.%20I%20am%20sitting%20here%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20and%20this%20would%20not%20have%20been%20necessary%20if%20talks%20had%20taken%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPathak%20said%20that%20going%20by%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20previous%20elections%2C%20it%20does%20not%20deserve%20even%20a%20single%20seat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCongress%20has%20zero%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20zero%20seats%20in%20the%20Delhi%20assembly.%20In%20the%20MCD%20%5BMunicipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%5D%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20Congress%20won%20nine%20wards%20out%20of%20250.%20If%20you%20see%20on%20a%20merit%20basis%20and%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20statistics%2C%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20deserve%20even%20one%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20only%20data%20is%20not%20important.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20the%20alliance%20dharma%20%5Band%20so%5D%20we%20offer%20them%20one%20seat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPathak%20said%20that%20the%20party%20is%20not%20announcing%20candidates%20for%20Delhi%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20will%20resume%20and%20results%20are%20arrived%20at%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20are%20still%20no%20results%2C%20then%20the%20six%20seats%20that%20we%20are%20aiming%20for%2C%20we%20will%20announce%20candidates%20for%20those%20seats%20as%20well%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fopposition-needs-a-roadmap-for-the-2024-elections%5C%22%3EOpposition%20Needs%20a%20Roadmap%20for%20the%202024%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CReady%20to%20fight%20on%20all%20seven%20seats%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EDelhi%20Congress%20chief%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%20said%20that%20the%20Delhi%20unit%20is%20%E2%80%9Cready%20and%20energised%E2%80%9D%20to%20fight%20on%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSeats%20are%20not%20decided%20through%20media%20channels%20and%20press%20conferences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20already%20has%20a%20committee%20under%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20that%20is%20looking%20at%20seat-sharing%20arrangements.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20Congress%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20are%20the%20only%20party%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20compared%20to%20both%20the%20AAP%20and%20BJP%2C%20that%20has%20conducted%20discussions%20of%20its%20workers%20on%20all%20seven%20parliamentary%20seats.%20Of%20the%20seven%20seats%2C%20in%20five%20we%20have%20already%20held%20big%20public%20meetings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20is%20the%20most%20prepared%20of%20all%20parties%20and%20our%20workers%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20elections.%20We%20were%20second%20on%20five%20out%20of%20the%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20elections.%20Because%20the%20Congress%20is%20the%20biggest%20party%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20alliance.%20The%20Delhi%20unit%20will%20abide%20by%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20Congress%20worker%20is%20ready%20and%20energised%20to%20fight%20on%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20Delhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFacing%20criticism%20from%20its%20allies%20for%20delaying%20seat-sharing%20talks%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20national%20leadership%20said%20that%20a%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20meeting%20was%20held%20at%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%20evening%20to%20finalise%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20admitted%20to%20a%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20admit%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20slight%20delay.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20difficult%20task%20because%20we%20are%20contesting%20against%20a%20few%20parties%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Ambikapur%2C%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%202024%20elections.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20we%20are%20fighting%20against%20the%20AAP%20and%20in%20Punjab%20%5Bas%20well%5D.%20But%20we%20are%2