ow%2F107665617.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20Attacks%20on%20Rafah%20Have%20Killed%20Dozens%20of%20Palestinians%20So%20Far%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F05165253%2FGFggzTzXUAA0kNa.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20More%20than%20100%20Palestinians%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20Monday%20as%20multiple%20locations%20in%20Rafah%20were%20attacked%20by%20the%20Israeli%20forces%2C%20according%20to%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20as%20per%20a%20CNN%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F12%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-airstrikes-rafah-ground-offensive-looms-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20strikes%20took%20place%20when%20Israeli%20forces%20rescued%20two%20hostages%20by%20storming%20a%20heavily%20guarded%20apartment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20conflicting%20reports%20on%20the%20death%20toll.%20As%20per%20an%20AP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-war-news-02-12-2024-4ade5edf47711c6b0c13d1380980de2b%3Ftaid%3D65c9f48be58ebf0001ba109b%26utm_campaign%3DTrueAnthem%26utm_medium%3DAP%26utm_source%3DTwitter%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ashraf%20al-Qidra%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Gaza%20Health%20Ministry%20said%20at%20least%2067%20people%20died%20in%20the%20strikes.%20In%20the%20Abu%20Youssef%20al-Najjar%20Hospital%20in%20Rafah%2C%20an%20AP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20journalist%20claims%20to%20have%20counted%20at%20least%2050%20bodies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDue%20to%20the%20overnight%20bombardment%20in%20Rafah%2C%20a%20large%20area%20of%20flattened%20houses%2C%20tattered%20tents%20and%20lines%20of%20bloodied%20bodies%20brought%20into%20nearby%20hospitals%20were%20visible%2C%20according%20to%20AP%20footage%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20population%20in%20Rafah%2C%20which%20borders%20Egypt%20is%201.4%20million.%20Israel%20describes%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20last%20remaining%20Hamas%20stronghold%20in%20the%20territory%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%202.3%20million%20population%20is%20in%20Rafah.%20As%20per%20a%20BBC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68274757%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20satellite%20images%20suggest%20that%20every%20open%20space%20in%20the%20city%20has%20been%20taken%20up%20by%20tents%20and%20other%20temporary%20shelters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-jv-just-exported-lethal-drones-to-israel-same-model-being-used-in-genocide-tainted-gaza-war%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202018%252C%2520Israel%2527s%2520Elbit%2520Systems%2Cfirst%2520time%2520outside%2520of%2520Israel.%5C%22%3EAdani%20JV%20Just%20Exported%20Lethal%20Drones%20to%20Israel%2C%20Same%20Model%20Being%20Used%20in%20Genocide-Tainted%20Gaza%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20AP%20report%2C%20Israeli%20military%20spokesman%20Rear%20Adm.%20Daniel%20Hagari%20quoted%20that%20special%20forces%20broke%20into%20a%20second-floor%20apartment%20in%20Rafah%20under%20fire%20at%201%3A49%20a.m.%20which%20was%20accompanied%20a%20minute%20later%20by%20airstrikes%20on%20surrounding%20areas.%20He%20claimed%20that%20members%20of%20the%20rescue%20team%20shielded%20the%20hostages%20with%20their%20bodies%20as%20Hamas%20were%20guarding%20the%20captives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Gaza%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20Health%20Ministry%2C%20m%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eore%20than%2012%2C300%20Palestinian%20children%20and%20young%20teens%20and%20about%208%2C400%20women%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20conflict%20so%20far%2C%20AP%20reported.%20Further%2C%20children%20and%20young%20teens%20com