Fa%3E%20a%20week%20ago%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EA%20momentous%20shift%20is%20under%20way%20in%20global%20markets%20as%20investors%20pull%20billions%20of%20dollars%20from%20China%E2%80%99s%20sputtering%20economy%2C%20two%20decades%20after%20betting%20on%20the%20country%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20growth%20story.%20Much%20of%20that%20cash%20is%20now%20heading%20for%20India%2C%20with%20Wall%20Street%20giants%20like%20Goldman%20Sachs%20and%20Morgan%20Stanley%20endorsing%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20as%20the%20prime%20investment%20destination%20for%20the%20next%20decade.%20That%20momentum%20is%20triggering%20a%20gold%20rush.%20Investors%20are%20paying%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20contrasting%20trajectories%20of%20two%20of%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20powers.%20India%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy%2C%20has%20vastly%20expanded%20infrastructure%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20his%20bid%20to%20lure%20global%20capital%20and%20supply%20lines%20away%20from%20Beijing.%20China%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20grappling%20with%20chronic%20economic%20woes%20and%20a%20widening%20rift%20with%20the%20Western-led%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20that%20followed%2C%20the%20article%20by%20Sivabalan%2C%20Chakraborty%20and%20Sircar%20was%20widely%20syndicated%20across%20platforms%20both%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20West.%20Sitting%20by%20chance%20next%20to%20a%20colleague%20on%20a%20flight%20back%20from%20Vegas%20the%20other%20day%2C%20the%20article%20immediately%20came%20up.%20It%20fits%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20moment%20so%20well.%20But%20what%20does%20it%20really%20tell%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobalization%20and%20deglobalization%20are%20complex%20phenomena.%20They%20involve%20multiple%20different%20dimensions%20of%20interaction%3A%20trade%2C%20direct%20productive%20investment%20and%20portfolio%20flows.%20Financial%20markets%20flows%20may%20tell%20a%20very%20different%20story%20than%20trade%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20comparing%20India%20and%20China%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20equating%20apples%20and%20oranges.%20In%20their%20combined%20and%20uneven%20development%2C%20India%20and%20China%20are%20in%20very%20different%20places.%20When%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20announces%20a%20target%20of%20an%2011%20percent%20increase%20in%20infrastructure%20spending%20to%20%24134%20billion%20for%202024%20it%20seems%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fed28192a-ee0d-4669-9087-2583d626ed60%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fed28192a-ee0d-4669-9087-2583d626ed60%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707907956072000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2bytNq3nT7GjWGU9tq43YT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebold%20step%20that%20sets%20markets%20alight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20the%20Indian%20economy%20measured%20at%20market%20exchange%20rates%20is%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fc3abd5bd-db16-4c00-a3f7-791e7f6a747b%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fc3abd5bd-db16-4c00-a3f7-791e7f6a747b%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707907956072000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2DrNTxVTGDVYXLwgbj0mvz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslightly%20larger%20than%20that%20of%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E.%20China%20is%20in%20a%20different%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20any%20case%20and%20inevitably%2C%20our%20assessment%20of%20these%20data%20are%20entangled%20with%20broader%20narratives%20and%20political%20positioning.%20In%20commentary%20on%20the%20future%20of%20CCP-run%20China%20there%20is%20no%20place%20of%20innocence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20loudest%20sources%20in%20the%20West%20on%20the%20state%20of%20China%20are%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20business%20people%20who%20have%20projects%20and%20wagers%20to%20promote%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20long%20or%20short%20China%2C%20and%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20China-watcher%20analysts%20and%20journalists%20many%20of%20whom%20can%20no%20longer%20safely%20return%20to%20China%20on%20account%20of%20their%20critical%20commentary%20and%20the%20repressive%20sanctions%20they%20might%20face.%20They%20write%20from%20the%20position%20of%20exile.%20Added%20to%20which%20we%20have%20the%20vantage%20point%20of%20India%2C%20which%20cannot%20help%20but%20be%20preoccupied%20with%20the%20question%20of%20who%20will%20be%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20%231.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20own%20position%20is%20that%20of%20a%20Western%20left%20liberal%20who%20broadly%20supports%20detente%20and%20peaceful%20adjustment%20of%20the%20world%20order%20and%20the%20Western%20%E2%80%9Cworldviews%E2%80%9D%20that%20go%20with%20it%2C%20to%20accommodate%20China%E2%80%99s%20rise%20and%20the%20broader%20shift%20towards%20a%20truly%20multipolar%20world.%20In%20so%20doing%2C%20I%20hold%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20distinguishing%2C%20as%20EU%20policy%20does%20for%20instance%2C%20between%20areas%20of%20cooperation%2C%20competition%20and%20rivalry.%20So%20I%20approach%20the%20dramatic%20narrative%20of%20transition%20pitched%20by%20the%20Bloomberg%20piece%20with%20a%20degree%20of%20skepticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20the%20Bloomberg%20piece%20in%20detail%20and%20what%20does%20the%20evidence%20consist%20of%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2462%20billion%20hedge%20fund%20Marshall%20Wace%20has%20positioned%20India%20as%20its%20biggest%20net%20long%20bet%20after%20the%20US%20in