%20globalization%3F%20And%20aside%20from%20the%20general%20story%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20crisis%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20what%20is%20the%20specific%20history%20of%20these%20financial%20flows%20and%20their%20significance%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViewed%20in%20broader%20terms%2C%20the%20dynamics%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20international%20economic%20integration%20right%20now%20are%20a%20picture%20of%20contrasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20trade%20surplus%20is%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F6b64131a-d1e1-42bb-bfd6-f4eef6ec76f7%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F6b64131a-d1e1-42bb-bfd6-f4eef6ec76f7%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707907956072000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2wjdYpyF3ETZiM-aViUaN2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehard%20to%20fully%20account%20for%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20is%20clearly%20gigantic%20and%20increasing%20in%20recent%20years.%20A%20figure%20of%20around%20%24800%20billion%20in%20surplus%20seems%20reasonable%20at%20the%20current%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20587px)%2085vw%2C%20587px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163650%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.33.46%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22587%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163650%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.33.46%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163650%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.33.46%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x224.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fupl