e.%20And%20it%20was%20only%20in%202020%20amidst%20the%20global%20crisis%20of%20COVID%20that%20non-resident%20portfolio%20investment%20in%20China%20came%20to%20dominate%20the%20entire%20EM%20scene.%20In%202020%20and%202021%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20in%20portfolio%20flows%20poured%20into%20China.%20This%20was%20completely%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163224%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.32.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163224%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.32.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163224%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.32.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x166.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163224%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.32.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x567.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696943%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20historic%20irony%20is%20that%20Wall%20Street%E2%80%99s%20very%20long-term%20play%20on%20China%20finally%20began%20to%20pay%20off%20precisely%20at%20the%20moment%20in%20which%20geopolitical%20tension%20made%20its%20continuation%20less%20and%20less%20tenable.%20As%20voices%20like%20Li%20Yuan%20and%20Lananh%20Nguyen%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F2b45d42d-d8ce-4928-b962-85cd6adc8f8e%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F2b45d42d-d8ce-4928-b962-85cd6adc8f8e%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707907956072000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1T6VbIsW2PVETJiyPK-8YM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoted%20in%20October%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F9b298f42-47ee-4b45-80a1-5c50fc67af05%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F9b298f42-47ee-4b45-80a1-5c50fc67af05%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMWc3ZDkifQ.ANHu2vRAyuFpjv7uiZBbU4uAYv19NWdGMb8wTAqqIz8%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707907956072000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2IFX0fNwHa1kdR0XQHlALv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENovember%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20was%20a%20stark%20contrast%20between%20Wall%20Street%E2%80%99s%20new%20infatuation%20with%20China%20and%20the%20mood%20both%20within%20China%20and%20on%20the%20broader%20global%20political%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20break%20came%20in%202022.%20The%20combination%20of%20surging%20inflation%2C%20interest%20rate%20hikes%20and%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20war%2C%20suddenly%20shifted%20the%20global%20mood.%20The%20talk%20was%20now%20of%20polycrisis.%20As%20the%20IIF%20data%20show%2C%20non-resident%20portfolio%20investment%20in%20EM%20generally%20collapsed.%20China%20was%20particularly%20hard%20hit.%20On%20an%20annualized%20basis%2C%20the%20swing%20from%20peak%20to%20trough%20in%20portfolio%20investment%20to%20China%20was%20a%20massive%20%24400%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20true%20for%20FDI%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20global%20geopolitical%20escalation%2C%20the%20disaster%20of%20Chinese%20COVID%20policy%20over%20the%20summer%20and%20fall%20of%202022%2C%20the%20implosion%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20market%2C%20and%20now%20the%20stock%20market%20rout%2C%20have%20made%20China%20extremely%20unattractive%20as%20a%20destination%20for%20capital%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20other%20EM%20are%20profiting.%20But%20portfolio%20flows%20to%20India%20were%20also%20subject%20to%20shocks%20%E2%80%93%20admittedly%20on%20a%20much%20smaller%20scale.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20in%20the%20aggregate%20data%20on%20portfolio%20flows%20in%202023%20for%20a%20surge%20into%20India%20in%20any%20way%20commensurate%20with%20the%20collapse%20in%20flows%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163049%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.30.42%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22636%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163049%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.30.42%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201090w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163049%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.30.42%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x205.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13163049%2FScreenshot-2024-02-13-at-4.30.42%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x699.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696942%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22434%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20authorities%20are%20not%20oblivious%20to%20the%20scale%20and%20impact%20of%20these%20shocks.%20They%20seem%20to%20be%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20obscure%20the%20scale%20of%20their%20gigantic%20trade%20surpluses%20and%20reserve%20accumulation.%20The%20FDI%20numbers%20are%20embarrassing%20and%20we%20should%20expect%20to%20see%20noises%20out%20of%20Beijing%20welcoming%20new%20investment.%20Beijing%20is%20also%20actively%20intervening%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20not%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20foreigners%20of%20course%2C%20but%20to%20avoid%20a%20disastrous%20blow%20to%20the%20wealth%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20upper%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20interventions%20are%20not%20targeted%20at%20foreign%20portfolio%20flows%2C%20the%20impact%20on%20foreign%20interests%20is%20real.%20In%20the%20days%20since%20the%20Bloomberg%20article%20on%20India%20appeared%2C%20there%20have%20been%20huge%20opportunistic%20flows%20into%20China%20equity%20funds%2C%20looking%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20official%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20worry%20on%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20part%20are%20not%20the%20relatively%20modest%20foreign%20portfolio%20flows.%20The%20real%20risk%20is%20that%20giant%20pools%20of%20Chinese%20wealth%20will%20start%20heading%20for%20the%20exit.%20It%20is%20not%20foreign%20jitters%20but%20a%20general%20panic%20and%20capital%20flight%20that%20is%20the%20real%20threat%20to%20Xi%E2%80%99s%20regime.%20It%20is%20not%20surprising%20to%20see%20a%20tightening%20of%20foreign%20exchange%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20essential%20point%20is%20that%20Beijing%20has%20always%20approached%20financial%20integration%20with%20the%20West%20cautiously.%20If%20portfolio%20investment%20takes%20a%20breather%2C%20Beijing%20will%20shrug.%20Western%20interests%20that%20play%20by%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20evolving%20rules%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20welcome.%20But%20China%20is%20not%20competing%20with%20India%20for%20the%20attentions%20of%20Western%20hedge%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAdam%20Tooze%20holds%20the%20Shelby%20Cullom%20Davis%20chair%20of%20History%20at%20Columbia%20University%20and%20serves%20as%20Director%20of%20the%20European%20Institute.%20A%20version%20of%20this%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20his%20newsletter%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F2%.06OBEWDZb4B0B03RUBV8eKVkEmH6r69jhdJgGaStigM%3F%5C%22%3EChartbook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20