andal%20in%20Adilabad%20district%2C%20Telangana%20has%20lost%20much%20of%20it%E2%80%99s%20sheen%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20cultural%20transformation%20but%20yet%20it%20is%20a%20big%20draw%20with%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETraditionally%2C%20a%20festival%20of%20Gond%20clan%20of%20tribes%20dependent%20on%20forest%2C%20it%20is%20now%20owned%20up%20by%20plain%20area%20tribals%20and%20even%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20festival%20commences%20annually%20on%20%3Cem%3EPushya%20Amavasya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(new%20moon)%20which%20fell%20on%20February%209%20this%20year.%20It%20lasts%20five%20days%20and%20Snake%20God%20is%20worshipped%2C%20the%20mythological%20divine%20force%20of%20the%20Raj%20Gonds%2C%20who%20considered%20the%20contiguous%20forest%20from%20then%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20including%20the%20present%20day%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20down%20to%20Chandrapur%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Adilabad%20their%20fiefdom%20six%20centuries%20ago.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20century%20later%20that%20different%20mythological%20stories%20have%20traced%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20festival%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20Mesram%20dynasty%20of%20Raj%20Gonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164720%2FE90C7B28-9003-4B1E-809D-D26D10449A4E.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164720%2FE90C7B28-9003-4B1E-809D-D26D10449A4E.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164720%2FE90C7B28-9003-4B1E-809D-D26D10449A4E-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164720%2FE90C7B28-9003-4B1E-809D-D26D10449A4E-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696958%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELocal%20residents%20and%20politicians%20participate%20in%20Nagoba%20Jatara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20customary%20practices%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rituals%20are%20held%20with%20an%20enormous%20snake%20inside%20a%20temple%20where%20members%20of%20Mesram%20dynasty%20alone%20are%20allowed%20to%20camp%20in%20make%20shift%20accommodation%20in%20the%20surroundings%20throughout%20the%20five%20days.%20Mythology%20has%20it%20that%20Nagoba%20who%20also%20went%20by%20the%20name%20Sesha%20Narayanamurthy%20appeared%20with%20hood%20open%20and%20danced%20from%20night%20fall%20to%20midnight%20on%20Pushya%20Amavasya.%20He%20drank%20milk%20offered%20by%20devotees%20and%20vanished.%20The%20moral%20of%20the%20story%20was%20that%20Nagoba%20shed%20light%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20devotees%20amidst%20pitch%20darkness%20caused%20by%20the%20new%20moon%20at%20his%20brief%20appearance.%20This%20was%20visible%20only%20to%20priests%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20festivities%20commence%20on%20full%20moon%2C%20a%20fortnight%20earlier%2C%20with%20one%20hundred%20and%20ten%20members%20of%20Mesram%20dynasty%20fetching%20holy%20water%20from%20river%20Godavari%20that%20passes%20by%20Jannaram%20forest%2C%20110%20kilometres%20away.%20Clad%20in%20all%20white%20with%20turban%20on%20head%2C%20they%20walk%20barefoot%20with%20earthen%20pots%20in%20a%20single%20file%20through%20rocky%20terrain%20and%20woods.%20It%20is%20a%20visual%20treat%20to%20watch%20the%20long%20stretch%20of%20walkers%20trekking%20in%20tandem%20in%20the%20Kawal%20tiger%20reserve%20as%20the%20sun%20sets%20over%20the%20western%20horizon%20and%20the%20sylvan%20stillness%20is%20shattered%20by%20the%20soft%20rustling%20of%20leaves%20amidst%20breeze.%20They%20collect%20water%20from%20the%20river%20in%20pots%20after%20performing%20the%20%3Ci%3Epooja%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20walk%20back%20on%20the%20same%20route%20till%20Indravelli%20where%20they%20halt%20to%20worship%20at%20the%20temple%20of%20Indradevi%2C%20related%20to%20Nagoba%2C%20before%20commencing%20for%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20their%20journey%20up%20to%20Keslapur%2C%20accompanied%20with%20drum%20beats%20and%20a%20band.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164900%2F93B8376A-2F58-446A-8238-E61E137D5F94.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22792%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164900%2F93B8376A-2F58-446A-8238-E61E137D5F94.jpeg%20792w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164900%2F93B8376A-2F58-446A-8238-E61E137D5F94-198x300.jpeg%20198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164900%2F93B8376A-2F58-446A-8238-E61E137D5F94-676x1024.jpeg%20676w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESnake%20God%20is%20worshipped%20during%20Nagoba%20Jatara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20walkers%20change%20the%20route%20every%20year%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20a%20wider%20section%20of%20Gonds%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20unite%20the%20tribe.%20This%20year%2C%20they%20covered%2028%20interior%20tribal%20habitations%20and%20a%20dozen%20villages%20having%20road%20network%20in%20five%20mandals.%20The%20villagers%20served%20them%20food%20and%20provided%20night%20shelter%20in%20keeping%20with%20tradition.%20Simultaneously%2C%20a%20separate%20group%20of%20men%20in%20white%20carry%20out%20a%20publicity%20campaign%20riding%20in%20bullock%20carts%20in%20villages%20for%20a%20week%20to%20announce%20the%20upcoming%20festival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fphotos-ladakh-changpa-festival-tribe-lac-restrictions%5C%22%3EIn%20Photos%3A%20A%20Glimpse%20Into%20Changpa%20Life%20at%20a%20Festival%20Close%20to%20the%20LAC%20in%20Ladakh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20water%20from%20river%20is%20used%20to%20clean%20the%20shrine%20of%20Nagoba%2C%20the%20idol%20of%20deity%20and%20the%20surroundings.%20When%20the%20elaborate%20rituals%20begin%20after%20night%20fall%2C%20the%20newly%20wed%20bridal%20couples%20of%20Mesram%20dynasty%20who%20are%20married%20in%20the%20year%20gone%20by%20are%20introduced%20to%20each%20other%20formally.%20Then%2C%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20temple%20are%20thrown%20open%20to%20public.%20The%20rituals%20are%20conducted%20by%20members%20of%20Pradhan%2C%20priest%20group%2C%20while%20all%20other%20services%20in%20the%20festival%20are%20rendered%20by%20the%20Kollam%20and%20Thoti%20groups.%20The%20families%20of%20Mesram%20dynasty%20take%20turns%20to%20cook%20food%20for%20themselves%20in%20hearths%20within%20the%20compound%20of%20the%20temple%20while%20others%20have%20to%20fend%20outside.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20noticeable%20changes%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20change%20in%20the%20rituals%20or%20other%20religious%20practices%20connected%20with%20the%20event%20but%20what%20was%20clearly%20visible%20was%20the%20character%20of%20gathering%20and%20the%20shift%20to%20enhance%20its%20sanctity%20with%20holy%20methods%20of%20worship.%20For%20instance%2C%20animal%20sacrifice%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20festival%20is%20now%20allowed%20at%20an%20isolated%20place%20away%20from%20the%20temple.%20The%20devotees%20are%20only%20allowed%20to%20break%20coconuts%20in%20front%20of%20the%20temple%20now%20as%20it%20is%20in%20the%20Hindu%20custom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20the%20%3Cem%3Edarbar%3C%2Fem%3E%20started%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20V.%20N.%20V.%20K.%20Sastry%2C%20retired%20director%20of%20Tribal%20Cultural%20Research%20and%20Training%20Institute%2C%20the%20festival%20was%20interrupted%20only%20twice%20in%20its%20long%20history.%20The%20first%20setback%20was%20on%20account%20of%20the%20encounter%20killing%20of%20legendary%20Gond%20leader%20Komuram%20Bheem%20by%20the%20army%20of%20nizam%20in%201940.%20Komuram%20Bheem%20waged%20a%20war%20against%20the%20tyranny%20of%20Nizam%20who%20ruled%20Hyderabad%20State%20by%20mobilising%20tribals%20to%20demand%20forest%20rights.%20He%20raised%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emava%20nate%2C%20mava%20raj%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(our%20village%2C%20our%20rule)%20as%20he%20pioneered%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jangal%2C%20jameen%3C%2Fem%3E%20struggle%20of%20tribals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERealising%20the%20virtue%20in%20the%20demand%2C%20nizam%20sent%20one%20of%20his%20ministers%20of%20British%20origin%20to%20meet%20noted%20anthropologist%20Fredrick%20von%20Furer%20Haimendorf%20at%20Copenhagen%20to%20mediate%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20win%20the%20confidence%20of%20tribals.%20Haimendorf%20who%20had%20discontinued%20his%20research%20in%20the%20north%20east%20due%20to%20restrictions%20imposed%20by%20the%20second%20world%20war%20accepted%20the%20invitation%20of%20Nizam%20after%20the%20latter%20gave%20him%20a%20firm%20assurance%20that%20he%20will%20have%20a%20smooth%20going.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaimendorf%20suggested%20the%20conduct%20of%20%3Cem%3Edarbar%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20one%20of%20the%20days%20as%20part%20of%20Nagoba%20jatara%20to%20hear%20their%20problems%20and%20resolve%20them%20instantly.%20The%20darbar%20was%20launched%20in%201942%20and%20continued%20till%20date%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20platform%20where%20officials%20from%20all%20government%20departments%20are%20present%20to%20interact%20with%20tribals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Haimendorf%20noted%20the%20grouse%20of%20Gonds%20that%20their%20traditions%20were%20overtaken%20by%20modernity.%20He%20also%20discussed%20that%20the%20Gonds%20were%20unhappy%20over%20losing%20exclusive%20rights%20to%20the%20festival%20with%20the%20intervention%20of%20Hindu%20culture%20in%20the%20rituals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13165030%2FEE3AAD19-D9FE-4876-BDF2-8DED3B7FF978.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13165030%2FEE3AAD19-D9FE-4876-BDF2-8DED3B7FF978.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13165030%2FEE3AAD19-D9FE-4876-BDF2-8DED3B7FF978-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13165030%2FEE3AAD19-D9FE-4876-BDF2-8DED3B7FF978-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696961%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETelangana%20tribal%20welfare%20minister%20Danasari%20Seethakka%20during%20Nagoba%20Jatara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20darbar%20was%20held%20on%20Monday%2C%20February%2012%20this%20time%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20tribal%20welfare%20minister%20Danasari%20Seethakka%2C%20local%20MLA%20Vedma%20Bojju%2C%20Adilabad%20collector%20Rahul%20Raj%20P.%20S.%2C%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Ghouse%20Alam%20and%20in-charge%20project%20officer%20of%20Integrated%20Tribal%20Development%20Agency%20(ITDA)%20at%20Utnoor%20Khushboo%20Gupta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20jatara%20was%20again%20disrupted%20after%20the%20infamous%20police%20firing%20on%20violent%20crowd%20at%20Indravelli%20in%201980.%20Thirteen%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20incident%20by%20official%20count%20but%20unofficial%20figure%20was%20over%20a%20hundred.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20a%20meeting%20organised%20by%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20War%20Group%20of%20Naxalites%2C%20the%20earlier%20name%20of%20CPI%20(Maoist)%2C%20during%20a%20weekly%20shandy%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-the-last-75-years-struggles-of-indias-tribal-communities-have-multiplied%5C%22%3E%20Over%20the%20Last%2075%20Years%2C%20Struggles%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Tribal%20Communities%20Have%20Multiplied%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20government%20constituted%20a%20committee%20of%20officials%20headed%20by%20ITDA%20PO%20M.%20V.%20P.%20C.%20Sastry%2C%20which%20successfully%20won%20over%20the%20tribals%20from%20a%20situation%20where%20there%20was%20a%20total%20breakdown%20in%20government%20%E2%80%93%20public%20interface.%20There%20was%20both%20fear%20and%20anger%20among%20tribals%2C%20Sastry%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20jatara%20in%20the%20past%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20tribal%20elder%20Thodsam%20Chandu%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20darbar%20was%20reduced%20to%20another%20political%20platform%20for%20leaders%20to%20harangue%20speeches%20and%20there%20was%20no%20resolution%20of%20demands%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20participants.%20The%20infrastructure%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20however%2C%20has%20vastly%20developed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707831018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13164510%2FE5B30BD1-21B5-429A-A3BF-97F35305FECC.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fin-telanganas-nagoba-jatara-hint-of-change-and-political-overtones%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20time%20while%20rituals%20and%20other%20religious%20practices%20connected%20with%20the%20event%20remained%20the%20same%2C%20what%20was%20clearly%20visible%20was%20the%20character%20of%20the%20gathering%20and%20the%20shift%20to%20enhance%20its%20sanctity%20with%20holy%20methods%20of%20worship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fin-telanganas-nagoba-jatara-hint-of-change-and-political-overtones%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%3A%20Congress%20Promises%20Right%20to%20MSP%20If%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Comes%20to%20Power%3B%20AAP%2C%20TMC%20Slam%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13183640%2FGGMm_W_W4AIfRaH.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20and%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20for%20using%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpolice-use-tear-gas-on-protesting-farmers-at-punjab-haryana-border%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etear%20gas%20shells%20and%20barricading%20roads%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20their%20%E2%80%9CDelhi%20Chalo%E2%80%9D%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20said%20that%20their%20commitment%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eannadatas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(food%20providers)%20has%20shone%20through%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20claim%20comes%20amidst%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%E2%80%99s%20post%20on%20Haryana%20Police%20testing%20tear%20gas%20drones%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20march.%20Several%20prominent%20social%20media%20accounts%20which%20were%20updating%20on%20the%20protests%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20withheld%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Haryana%20Police%20today%20tested%20tear%20gas%20shell-dropping%20drone%20system%20at%20Shambhu%20border%20near%20Ambala%2C%20in%20view%20of%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20farmers%20protest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F333ZMuSoUe%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F333ZMuSoUe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1757045332486049835%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20his%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Ambikapur%20announced%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20give%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20in%20the%20country%20are%20not%20getting%20what%20they%20should%20get.%20Farmers%20are%20marching%20to%20Delhi%20but%20they%20are%20being%20stopped%2C%20tear%20gas%20shells%20are%20being%20fired%20on%20them%20and%20they%20are%20being%20jailed.%20What%20are%20the%20farmers%20saying%3F%20Just%20that%20we%20should%20get%20the%20fruits%20of%20our%20hard%20work.%20The%20BJP%20gave%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20M.S.%20Swaminathan.%20But%20the%20cause%20to%20which%20Swaminathan%20devoted%20his%20life%2C%20his%20recommendations%20on%20MSP%2C%20they%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20do.%20Swaminathan%20report%20clearly%20said%20that%20farmers%20should%20get%20MSP%20as%20a%20legal%20right.%20But%20BJP%20is%20not%20doing%20this.%20If%20INDIA%20alliance%20forms%20the%20government%20we%20will%20give%20MSP%E2%80%99s%20legal%20guarantee%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20gathering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20be%20remembered%20in%20history%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Ccruelty%2C%20barbarity%2C%20repression%20and%20oppression%20against%20farmers%E2%80%9D%20and%20questioned%20why%20they%20are%20being%20stopped%20from%20coming%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20history%20is%20written%2C%20the%2010-year%20tenure%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20be%20known%20as%20the%20period%20of%20cruelty%2C%20barbarity%2C%20repression%20and%20oppression%20against%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20suppress%20the%20voice%20of%20farmers%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20converted%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Delhi%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98police%20cantonment%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20if%20an%20enemy%20has%20attacked%20the%20power%20in%20Delhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeavy%20security%20has%20been%20deployed%20along%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%20including%20barricades%20and%20barbed%20wire.%20Prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144%20have%20also%20been%20imposed%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Haryana%20police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20as%20farmers%20broke%20barricades%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20continue%20their%20march.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20call%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20and%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20led%20by%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20other%20unions%20demanding%20for%20a%20law%20on%20the%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%2C%20withdrawing%20criminal%20cases%20filed%20during%20the%202020%20farm%20protest%2C%20a%20farm%20loan%20waiver%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ftalks-with-union-ministers-inconclusive-farmers-stick-with-plan-to-march-to-delhi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emeeting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ebetween%20Union%20ministers%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20held%20on%20Monday%20to%20prevent%20a%202020-21%20like%20agitation%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20failed%20to%20yield%20a%20consensus%20with%20the%20farmers%20deciding%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20its%20promises%20to%20farmers%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20including%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%2C%20implementing%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20on%20MSP%2C%20and%20providing%20legal%20status%20to%20MSP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWest%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20also%20lent%20her%20support%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20said%20that%20the%20agitation%20exposes%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cfailure%20to%20support%20farmers%20and%20labourers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20our%20country%20progress%20when%20the%20farmers%20are%20attacked%20with%20tear%20gas%20shells%20for%20fighting%20for%20their%20basic%20rights%3F%20I%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20brutal%20assault%20on%20our%20farmers%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Govt.%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20support%20farmers%20and%20labourers%2C%20coupled%20with%20futile%20PR%20stunts%2C%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20(%40MamataOfficial)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMamataOfficial%2Fstatus%2F1757317025628881196%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Banerjee%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbrutal%20assault%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20our%20country%20progress%20when%20the%20farmers%20are%20attacked%20with%20tear%20gas%20shells%20for%20fighting%20for%20their%20basic%20rights%3F%20I%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20brutal%20assault%20on%20our%20farmers%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Central%20Government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20support%20farmers%20and%20labourers%2C%20coupled%20with%20futile%20PR%20stunts%2C%20exposes%20the%20illusion%20of%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat.%E2%80%99%20Instead%20of%20suppressing%20their%20protest%2C%20BJP%20must%20focus%20on%20humbling%20their%20inflated%20egos%2C%20power-hungry%20ambitions%2C%20and%20inadequate%20governance%20that%20has%20harmed%20our%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday%20denied%20permission%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20convert%20the%20Bawana%20stadium%20into%20a%20temporary%20jail%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20from%20Delhi%20home%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%20are%20%E2%80%9Cgenuine%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20every%20citizen%20has%20the%20Constitutional%20right%20to%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAAP%E2%80%99s%20new%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%20has%20also%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Modi%20urging%20him%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpersonally%20intervene%E2%80%9D%20and%20lend%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccompassionate%20ear%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20recent%20recognition%20of%20Shri%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20and%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20has%20brought%20a%20moment%20of%20pride%20for%20our%20agricultural%20community.%20However%20%2C%20it%20is%20disheartening%20to%20witness%20the%20same%20community%20now%20facing%20tear%20gas%20and%20impediments%20on%20their%20journey%20to%20secure%20their%20rightful%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%3A%20Annadata%20Samman%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20remained%20steadfast%20in%20its%20commitment%20to%20farmers%20through%20its%20policies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAlong%20with%20Nari%20Shakti%2C%20Yuva%20Shakti%2C%20Annadatas%20have%20been%20the%20pillar%20for%20which%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20been%20working%20for%20in%20a%20steadfast%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shazia%20Ilmi%2C%20national%20spokesperson%2C%20BJP%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20implemented%20policies%20for%20farmers%20benefits%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20giving%20health%20cards%2C%20provision%20of%20loans%20at%20low%20interests%20or%20samman%20rashi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20promise%20to%20legalise%20MSP%2C%20Ilmi%20questioned%20why%20the%20party%20had%20not%20implemented%20it%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20posted%20multiple%20times%20on%20its%20X%20account%2C%20highlighting%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20empowering%20farmers%20through%20its%20schemes%20with%20the%20hashtag%20AnnadataKaSamman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20government%20is%20fully%20committed%20to%20providing%20100%20percent%20benefits%20of%20the%20schemes%20to%20the%20farmer%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20one%20post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20posts%2C%20it%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20increased%20the%20MSP%20on%20wheat%2C%20barley%2C%20masoor%2C%20channa%20among%20others%20in%20comparison%20to%20what%20was%20being%20provided%20prior%20to%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20that%20farmers%20had%20become%20%E2%80%9Cself-reliant%20due%20to%20increase%20in%20food%20production%20capacity%20during%20the%20Modi%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707829754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13183640%2FGGMm_W_W4AIfRaH.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffarmers-congress-promises-right-to-msp-if-india-bloc-comes-to-power-aap-tmc-slam-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20party's%20claim%20that%20it%20is%20with%20'annadatas'%20comes%20amidst%20reports%20that%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20is%20testing%20tear%20gas%20drones%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20march.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffarmers-congress-promises-right-to-msp-if-india-bloc-comes-to-power-aap-tmc-slam-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Electoral%20Choices%20Do%20Indian%20Muslims%20Have%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-