u%20can%20only%20imagine%20why%20the%20lunch%20is%20a%20kaleidoscope%20of%20flavours%2C%20the%20colours%20paralleling%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20place%20itself.%20The%20Konkan%20influence%20is%20visible%20in%20each%20dish%20and%20fish%20is%20the%20obvious%20hero%20with%20curries%20and%20fried%20delights%20that%20bring%20out%20its%20flavour%20to%20perfection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sawantwadi%20Palace%20Hotel%20is%20bliss%20in%20all%20its%20splendid%20geometry.%20And%20I%20am%20still%20reeling%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20royalty%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20can%20testify%20that%20neither%20the%20grandeur%20of%20the%20Sawantwadi%20Palace%20Hotel%20nor%20the%20beautiful%20shades%20it%20turns%20as%20the%20sun%20sets%20can%20parallel%20the%20warmth%20of%20this%20couple%20who%20says%20all%20they%20want%20to%20do%20is%20dream%20bigger%20and%20carry%20the%20legacy%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707826375000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341653%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Run%20by%20Yuvraj%20Lakham%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%20and%20Yuvrani%20Shraddha%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%2C%20the%20Sawantwadi%20Palace%20Hotel%20is%20a%20unique%20Konkan%20homestay%20inspired%20by%20the%20ancient%20card%20game%20of%20ganjifa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341653%2Funique-homestay-in-goa-maharashtra-sawantwadi-palace-hotel-run-by-royal-family-sawant-bhonsle%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashok%20Chavan%3A%20BJP%20Makes%20Peace%20With%20Another%20Scam%20As%20Congress%20Battles%20Series%20of%20Exits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13172548%2FGE6o8Aka4AABHBz.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20day%20after%20quitting%20Congress%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20has%20now%20announced%20his%20entry%20into%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAppearing%20to%20underplay%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20a%20party%20which%20his%20family%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20for%20over%20five%20decades%20%E2%80%93%20Chavan%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20like%20to%20%E2%80%9Cget%20into%20a%20blame%20game%E2%80%9D%20and%20did%20not%20give%20a%20reason%20for%20his%20exit%2C%20instead%20saying%20he%20has%20now%20begun%20a%20new%20political%20journey%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChavan%20is%2065.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20him%2C%20another%20Congress%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20legislative%20council%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Nanded%2C%20Amar%20Rajurkar%2C%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Rajurkar%20was%20also%20present%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mumbai%20which%20was%20jointly%20addressed%20by%20Chavan%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFadnavis%20announced%20that%20many%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20dormant%20scam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavan%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20for%20two%20short%20stints%20between%202008%20and%202010%2C%20had%20to%20abruptly%20step%20down%20following%20allegations%20of%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20Adarsh%20Co-operative%20Housing%20Society%20scam.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20had%20named%20him%20as%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20beneficiaries%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbombay-high-court-orders-demolition-of-adarsh-building-but-stays-order-for-three-months%5C%22%3Ea%2031-storey%20building%20which%20was%20originally%20built%20for%201999%20Kargil%20war%20heroes%20and%20fallen%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20war%20widows%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20had%20claimed%20that%20due%20to%20the%20violation%20of%20several%20rules%2C%20three%20of%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20relatives%20secured%20flats%20in%20this%20upmarket%20housing%20property%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Cuffe%20Parade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20since%20Chavan%20was%20named%20in%20the%20scam.%20The%20case%20has%20since%20remained%20dormant%2C%20with%20some%20of%20the%20primary%20accused%20of%20the%20case%20having%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FSpecials%2FlRcWV2Oa7UuS7JvuVe4ceK%2FAdarsh-scam-main-accused-Kanhaiyalal-Gidwani-64-dies.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edied%20in%20the%20meantime%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20raked%20this%20issue%20up%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202014%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%2C%20Adarsh%20grew%20into%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20poll%20planks%20for%20the%20party.%20And%20as%20recently%20as%20last%20week%2C%20when%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20released%20its%20%E2%80%9Cwhite%20paper%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20the%20Adarsh%20scam%20once%20again%20found%20a%20mention%20under%20the%20section%20%E2%80%9Cpervasive%20corruption%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcentre-tables-white-paper-on-10-years-of-upa-hours-after-congresss-black-paper-on-modi-govts-failures%5C%22%3ECentre%20Tables%20White%20Paper%20on%2010%20Years%20of%20UPA%2C%20Hours%20After%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Black%20Paper%20on%20Modi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Failures%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20including%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20have%20attributed%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20party%20to%20the%20pending%20trial%20in%20the%20case.%20Chavan%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mumbai%20soon%20after%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20called%20the%20Adarsh%20scam%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20accident%E2%80%9D.%20He%20denied%20any%20links%20between%20the%20scam%20and%20to%20his%20decision%20of%20quitting%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20series%20of%20exits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavan%20is%20the%20third%20big%20name%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20after%20Milind%20Deora%20and%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20to%20exit%20the%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20While%20Deora%20went%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Siddique%20hopped%20onto%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party.%20Reacting%20to%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20BJP%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-chavan-called-me-baba-siddique-reveals-why-ex-cm-quit-congress-joined-bjp-101707818738288.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESiddique%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20this%20should%20come%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwake%20up%20call%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20senior%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%2C%20blamed%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leadership%20for%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20exit.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavan%E2%80%99s%20possible%20move%20to%20the%20BJP%20had%20been%20known%20for%20a%20while%20now.%20Nirupam%2C%20without%20mentioning%20any%20names%2C%20claimed%20that%20Chavan%20quit%20the%20party%20only%20because%20he%20was%20troubled%20by%20one%20particular%20party%20functionary.%20It%20is%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20guess%20that%20Nirupam%20was%20speaking%20about%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20fact%2C%20all%20party%20leaders%20who%20spoke%20in%20favour%20of%20Chavan%20have%20blamed%20Patole%20for%20his%20style%20of%20running%20the%20party.%20Patole%2C%20who%20crossed%20over%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20strained%20relationship%20with%20most%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20exit%2C%20Patole%20said%20on%20Monday%20(February%2012)%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20has%20given%20a%20lot%20to%20many%20leaders.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20today%2C%20when%20the%20party%20is%20fighting%20to%20save%20democracy%20and%20the%20constitution%2C%20leaders%20who%20have%20got%20everything%20from%20it%20are%20quitting%20the%20party%20and%20its%20ideology.%20Who%20is%20going%20where%2C%20for%20what%3F%20The%20public%20is%20watching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20To%20this%2C%20Chavan%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20given%20a%20lot%20to%20me%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20I%20have%20given%20a%20lot%20to%20the%20Congress%20party.%20This%20truth%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20denied.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20party%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%2C%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20in-charge%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mumbai%20said%20that%20the%20party%20gave%20him%20enough%20opportunities%20and%20built%20his%20career.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20party%2C%20he%20%5BChavan%5D%20decided%20to%20run%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChennithala%20also%20mentioned%20that%20until%20a%20day%20before%20Chavan%20exited%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20he%20was%20present%20at%20all%20party%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20Chavan%20even%20met%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20just%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20If%20Chavan%20had%20issued%20with%20the%20party%20functioning%2C%20he%20should%20have%20simply%20voiced%20it.%20A%20leader%20as%20senior%20as%20Chavan%20is%20expected%20to%20voice%20his%20opinion%20freely.%20Leaders%20have%20that%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chennithala%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Chavan%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20a%20single%20reason%20for%20his%20exit.%20%E2%80%9CI%20heard%20him%20%5BChavan%5D%20speak%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%20He%20had%20no%20grounds%20to%20provide.%20If%20it%20is%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%2C%20what%20can%20we%20say%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatole%2C%20who%20was%20also%20at%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20urged%20Chavan%20to%20return%20to%20the%20party.%20%E2%80%9CStill%2C%20nothing%20has%20gone%20bad%20between%20him%20and%20the%20party%20leaders%2C%20I%20urge%20Chavan%20to%20return%20to%20the%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20last%20year%2C%20Chavan%20had%20met%20Kharge%20and%20sought%20changes%20within%20the%20party%20to%20ensure%20better%20results%20in%20the%202024%20election.%20Following%20this%2C%20he%20was%20inducted%20in%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20senior%20leader%2C%20Balasaheb%20Thorat%2C%20had%20to%20vacate%20his%20post%20to%20make%20way%20for%20Chavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20December%202023%2C%20Chavan%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20Maharashtra%20within%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA).%20Patole%20said%20Chavan%20has%20always%20liked%20to%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20and%20hold%20the%20position%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20known%20him%20for%20long.%20He%20has%20always%20liked%20to%20be%20a%20leader.%20But%20he%20should%20know%20that%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20would%20get%20no%20such%20opportunity.%20He%20will%20have%20to%20be%20in%20the%20backseat%20from%20now%20on.%E2%80%9D%20Patole%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavan%20is%20also%20the%20third%20prominent%20Maratha%20leader%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Before%20him%2C%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20both%20jumped%20boats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20tried%20hard%20to%20woo%20the%20Maratha%20community%20that%20is%20both%20numerically%20and%20politically%20dominant%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%20also%20meant%20alienation%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20in%20the%20party.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20prominent%20leader%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%2C%20who%20had%20left%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20to%20join%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20is%20openly%20expressing%20his%20discontent%20with%20the%20BJP.%20He%20even%20rendered%20his%20resignation%2C%20which%20the%20coalition%20government%20has%20not%20acted%20upon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707825546000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13172548%2FGE6o8Aka4AABHBz.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fashok-chavan-adarsh-scam-congress-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20decade%20and%20half%20since%20the%20former%20Congress%20leader%20was%20named%20in%20the%20scam%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20raked%20this%20issue%20up%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20It%20even%20found%20mention%20in%20its%20government's%20recent%20'white%20paper'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fashok-chavan-adarsh-scam-congress-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20puts%20Estonian%20PM%20on%20wanted%20list%20for%20'desecration%20of%20historical%20memory'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707821462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107660778%2Cimgsize-593284.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-puts-estonian-pm-on-wanted-list-for-desecration-of-historical-memory%2Farticleshow%2F107660433.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107660433.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERussian%20police%20have%20put%20Estonian%20prime%20minister%20Kaja%20Kallas%2C%20Estonian%20state%20secretary%20Taimar%20Peterkop%2C%20and%20Lithuanian%20Culture%20Minister%20Simonas%20Kairys%20on%20the%20wanted%20list%20for%20%26quot%3Bdesecration%20of%20historical%20memory%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdestroying%20monuments%20to%20Soviet%20soldiers%26quot%3B.%20Baltic%20nations%20plan%20to%20demolish%20Soviet-era%20monuments.%20Several%20dozen%20Baltic%20politicians%20are%20also%20wanted%20by%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-puts-estonian-pm-on-wanted-list-for-desecration-of-historical-memory%2Farticleshow%2F107660433.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-puts-estonian-pm-on-wanted-list-for-desecration-of-historical-memory%2Famp_articleshow%2F107660433.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-puts-estonian-pm-on-wanted-list-for-desecration-of-historical-memory%2Famp_articleshow%2F107660433.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tear%20gas%20dropped%20from%20drones%20as%20protesting%20farmers%20march%20towards%20Indian%20capital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707820500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-farmers-protest-delhi_6453843.jpg%3F20240213083719%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Findia-tear-gas-dropped-from-drones-as-protesting-farmers-march-towards-new-delhi-13070593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20200%20farmers'%20unions%20have%20called%20on%20their%20supporters%20to%20march%20to%20the%20Indian%20capital%20to%20protest%20against%20unfulfilled%20demands%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20issues%20including%20prices%20and%20pensions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Findia-tear-gas-dropped-from-drones-as-protesting-farmers-march-towards-new-delhi-13070593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Falls%20Short%20in%20Advancing%20Gender%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111222%2Fimage-1824.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20critiques%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fempowerment-or-exploitation-how-uniform-civil-code-will-impact-womens-rights-in-india%2Farticle67109276.ece%5C%22%3Ewomen%E2%80%99s%20organisations%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Faidwa-strongly-opposes-ucc-letter-law-commission%5C%22%3Eand%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeoplesdemocracy.in%2F2023%2F0716_pd%2Faidwa-memorandum-law-commission-uniform-civil-code%5C%22%3Ehave%20opposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC).%20They%20have%20emphasised%20that%20merely%20having%20uniform%20laws%20will%20not%20guarantee%20women%20equal%20rights%20or%20eradicate%20the%20discrimination%20inherent%20in%20various%20patriarchal%20and%20discriminatory%20personal%20laws.%20They%20argue%20that%20uniformity%20alone%20does%20not%20ensure%20equality%20and%20cannot%20be%20equated%20with%20either%20progressive%20legislation%20or%20justice%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20highlighted%20the%20disappointing%20history%20of%20reform%20initiated%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government.%20They%20said%20it%20had%20never%20prioritised%20gender%20justice.%20Despite%20numerous%20demands%2C%20such%20as%20reforming%20inequitable%20aspects%20of%20Hindu%20Personal%20Laws%2C%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20a%20UCC%20under%20the%20current%20regime%20may%20merely%20replicate%20existing%20Hindu%20Laws%2C%20rather%20than%20advancing%20gender%20justice.%20They%20argue%20that%20the%20aim%20of%20the%20UCC%20under%20the%20Modi%20government%20seems%20to%20target%20Muslims%20and%20Muslim%20Personal%20Laws%2C%20which%20the%20government%20has%20consistently%20criticised%20since%20coming%20into%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20proposed%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%20intentionally%20excludes%20the%20Adivasi%20community%2C%20who%20constitute%203%25%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20demonstrates%20insensitivity%20towards%20both%20the%20progressive%20elements%20of%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20and%20the%20discriminatory%20aspects%20of%20Hindu%20Personal%20Law.%20Certain%20provisions%20added%20to%20the%20proposed%20Bill%20are%20regressive%2C%20discriminatory%2C%20and%20unconstitutional.%20Additionally%2C%20while%20ostensibly%20acknowledging%20live-in-relationships%20between%20consenting%20heterosexual%20adults%2C%20the%20Bill%20violates%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20privacy%20and%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20a%20partner.%20It%20imposes%20impractical%20conditions%20on%20these%20relationships%20by%20mandating%20registration%20and%20subjecting%20them%20to%20open%20%E2%80%9Cscrutiny%E2%80%9D%2C%20under%20vague%20standards%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20policy%20and%20morality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetrogressive%20provisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20provisions%20of%20the%20UCC%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20duplication%20of%20those%20in%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%20(HMA)%20of%201955%20and%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20(SMA)%2C%20with%20some%20exceptions.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20conditions%20for%20entering%20into%20a%20marriage%20closely%20resemble%20those%20outlined%20in%20the%20HMA%20and%20SMA.%20However%2C%20a%20retrogressive%20provision%20says%20that%20parties%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20marry%20within%20certain%20prohibited%20relationships%20unless%20the%20custom%20or%20usage%20of%20one%20of%20them%20permits%20such%20a%20marriage.%20It%20further%20says%20that%20these%20customs%20and%20usage%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20order%20and%20morality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20the%20field%20open%20for%20the%20courts%20to%20interpret%20public%20policy%20and%20morality%20according%20to%20their%20way%20of%20thinking%20and%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grounds%20for%20judicial%20separation%20and%20divorce%20are%20the%20same%20as%20those%20in%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20and%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20except%20that%20the%20divorce%20provisions%20have%20been%20widened%20to%20lay%20down%20another%20retrogressive%20additional%20ground%20which%20says%20that%20if%20either%20spouse%20converts%20to%20another%20religion%2C%20the%20other%20spouse%20can%20ask%20for%20a%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20anti-human%20rights%20provision%20that%20allows%20for%20a%20claim%20for%20restitution%20of%20conjugal%20rights%20has%20also%20been%20retained%20in%20this%20Code.%20This%20right%20is%20an%20outdated%20and%20unconstitutional%20provision%20of%20English%20Law%2C%20which%20allows%20one%20party%20to%20the%20marriage%20to%20ask%20the%20court%20to%20restore%20his%20or%20her%20conjugal%20rights%20to%20the%20other%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sections%20on%20interim%20maintenance%20and%20permanent%20alimony%20have%20also%20been%20mechanically%20replicated.%20If%20there%20had%20been%20any%20intentions%20to%20advance%20or%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20separated%20and%20deserted%20women%2C%20who%20are%20forced%20into%20lengthy%20legal%20battles%2C%20at%20least%20the%20widely%20accepted%20criteria%20for%20awarding%20maintenance%20could%20have%20been%20written%20into%20the%20law.%20Indian%20courts%20have%20laid%20down%20that%20the%20maintenance%2C%20which%20should%20be%20awarded%20by%20the%20court%2C%20should%20be%20commensurate%20with%20the%20standards%20of%20living%20of%20the%20parties.%20The%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act%20also%20lays%20down%20that%20the%20amount%20granted%20to%20a%20woman%20as%20monetary%20relief%20should%20be%20adequate%2C%20fair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20consistent%20with%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20to%20which%20the%20aggrieved%20person%20is%20accustomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20has%20not%20been%20done.%20Women%20have%20to%20fight%20a%20long%2C%20weary%20battle%20in%20the%20courts%20to%20receive%20an%20extremely%20inadequate%20sum%20as%20maintenance.%20While%20the%20section%20on%20interim%20maintenance%20says%20that%20this%20should%20be%20decided%20within%20two%20months%20of%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20application%2C%20this%20seldom%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdded%20to%20this%20is%20the%20burden%20of%20proving%20the%20income%20of%20the%20husband%2C%20which%20is%20impossible%20for%20most%20wives.%20Some%20courts%20deny%20maintenance%20to%20a%20woman%20if%20she%20leaves%20the%20home%20or%20is%20seen%20at%20fault.%20The%20law%20should%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20maintenance%20is%20not%20a%20largesse%20granted%20by%20the%20court%2C%20but%20is%20one%20of%20the%20rights%20that%20a%20woman%20has%20acquired%20by%20contributing%20to%20the%20household.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20these%20issues%20have%20been%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20sections%20for%20permanent%20alimony%20should%20have%20been%20reframed%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20women%20to%20actually%20get%20the%20alimony.%20The%20fact%20that%20none%20of%20these%20issues%20were%20tackled%2C%20shows%20that%20the%20intention%20of%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20code%20was%20not%20to%20bring%20greater%20gender%20justice%20but%20to%20force%20a%20majoritarian%20UCC%20on%20all%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2035%20on%20custody%20of%20children%20is%20the%20same%20as%20that%20in%20the%20HMA%20and%20SMA.%20However%2C%20a%20sub-section%202%20has%20been%20added%2C%20in%20which%20the%20court%20has%20been%20enjoined%20to%20keep%20the%20best%20interest%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20child%20as%20a%20paramount%20consideration.%20A%20condition%20has%20also%20been%20added%20to%20sub-section%202%20that%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20minor%20child%20of%20less%20than%20five%20years%20shall%20ordinarily%20be%20with%20the%20mother.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20though%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20code%20could%20have%20made%20both%20the%20mother%20and%20father%20equal%20guardians%20of%20the%20child%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20so%20despite%20this%20being%20a%20demand%20for%20a%20long%20time%20by%20various%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhat-a-gender-just-uniform-civil-code-could-look-like%5C%22%3EWhat%20a%20Gender-Just%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Could%20Look%20Like%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20retrogressive%20section%20in%20the%20UCC%20talks%20of%20disposal%20of%20the%20estate%20of%20either%20party%20and%20states%20that%20the%20court%20may%20decide%20to%20make%20such%20provisions%20for%20the%20estate%20as%20it%20deems%20just%20and%20proper%20in%20favour%20of%20either%20party.%20For%20some%20time%20now%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20organisations%20and%20groups%20have%20been%20demanding%20equal%20rights%20to%20marital%20property%20for%20women.%20Marital%20property%20refers%20to%20assets%20acquired%20either%20jointly%20or%20individually%20by%20the%20parties%20during%20the%20course%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20law%2C%20as%20it%20stands%20now%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20the%20share%20of%20women%20in%20the%20property%20bought%20by%20the%20parties%20and%20gives%20it%20to%20the%20person%20in%20whose%20name%20the%20property%20has%20been%20bought.%20This%20often%20means%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20left%20without%20any%20assets%20of%20the%20household%20when%20a%20breakdown%20of%20a%20marriage%20occurs%2C%20since%20women%20are%20seldom%20the%20named%20owners.%20A%20recent%20Madras%20high%20court%20judgment%20recognised%20the%20productive%20and%20equal%20value%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20household%20work%20and%20held%20that%20she%20was%20entitled%20to%20an%20equal%20share%20of%20the%20assets%20on%20separation.%20However%2C%20the%20UCC%2C%20instead%20of%20recognising%20women%E2%80%99s%20marital%20property%20rights%2C%20has%20made%20a%20neutral%20provision%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20advance%20gender%20justice%20and%20can%20be%20misused%20by%20unscrupulous%20spouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20Muslims%20is%20evident%20through%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20UCC.%20While%20there%20has%20been%20a%20demand%20from%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20outlaw%20Halala%2C%20the%20Code%20takes%20a%20further%20step%20by%20criminalising%20it.%20This%20mirrors%20the%20approach%20of%20the%20Triple%20Talaq%20legislation%20(The%20Muslim%20Women%20Protection%20of%20Rights%20on%20Marriage%20Act%2C%202019)%2C%20which%20punishes%20a%20Muslim%20male%20for%20pronouncing%20instant%20Triple%20Talaq%20with%20imprisonment.%20Thus%2C%20while%20no%20man%20from%20any%20other%20community%20faces%20punishment%20for%20unjustly%20leaving%20or%20deserting%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20has%20made%20a%20Muslim%20man%20guilty%20of%20a%20criminal%20offence%20punishable%20by%20imprisonment%20merely%20for%20leaving%20his%20wife%20by%20pronouncing%20triple%20talaq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20the%20present%20Act%2C%20if%20a%20person%20compels%2C%20abets%2C%20or%20induces%20(terms%20that%20are%20somewhat%20vague%20and%20can%20be%20broadly%20interpreted)%20another%20person%20to%20practice%20%3Cem%3ENikah%20Halala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20they%20can%20be%20sentenced%20to%20up%20to%20three%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20fined%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Furthermore%2C%20a%20marriage%20cannot%20be%20dissolved%20under%20the%20Code%20except%20in%20accordance%20with%20its%20provisions%2C%20and%20a%20draconian%20provision%20has%20unreasonably%20and%20unjustly%20made%20a%20violation%20of%20this%20punishable%20by%20up%20to%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20imprisonment%20and%20a%20fine.%20Presumably%2C%20this%20section%20has%20been%20framed%20to%20prevent%20extrajudicial%20divorces%20in%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20unilateral%20right%20of%20divorce%20that%20is%20available%20to%20the%20Muslim%20man%2C%20divorce%20in%20Muslim%20law%20can%20also%20be%20done%20through%20mutual%20consent.%20The%20wife%20under%20Muslim%20law%20also%20has%2C%20unlike%20any%20woman%20in%20any%20other%20law%2C%20a%20right%20to%20ask%20for%20%3Ci%3EKhula%3C%2Fi%3E%20(divorce)%20and%20to%20be%20granted%20it.%20This%20has%20been%20pronounced%20to%20be%20an%20inalienable%20right%20of%20Muslim%20women%20to%20ask%20for%20unilateral%20separation.%20Thus%2C%20parts%20of%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%2C%20which%20benefitted%20Muslim%20women%2C%20have%20also%20been%20done%20away%20with%2C%20which%20requires%20all%20persons%20to%20go%20through%20a%20lengthy%20prolonged%20litigation%20for%20divorce%20only%20on%20the%20grounds%20based%20on%20the%20fault%20of%20the%20other%20spouse%20stipulated%20in%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%20and%20Special%20Marriage%20Act.%20For%20no%20good%20reasons%2C%20the%20practice%20of%20%3Cem%3Eiddat%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20been%20discontinued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-and-the-ucc-the-fear-of-majoritarianism-is-real-and-cant-be-brushed-aside%5C%22%3EMuslims%20and%20the%20UCC%3A%20The%20Fear%20of%20Majoritarianism%20Is%20Real%20and%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Be%20Brushed%20Aside%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provisions%20relating%20to%20succession%20in%20the%20code%20are%20also%20those%20which%20are%20applicable%20to%20Hindus%20under%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%20and%20the%20Indian%20Succession%20Act%20which%20talks%20of%20the%20general%20laws%20relating%20to%20Wills%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20succession%20to%20the%20estates%20of%20Christians%20and%20Parsis.%20However%2C%20some%20beneficial%20provisions%20of%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20which%20restrict%20the%20right%20to%20Will%20to%20only%20one-third%20of%20the%20property%20away%20from%20heirs%20have%20not%20been%20recognised.%20The%20right%20to%20Will%20all%20one%E2%80%99s%20property%20has%20been%20taken%20from%20English%20Law.%20However%2C%20some%20European%20and%20others%20countries%20have%20put%20restrictions%20on%20the%20right%20to%20Will%20to%20safeguard%20heirs.%20Women%20in%20India%20have%20been%20demanding%20this%20right%20so%20that%20the%20property%20is%20not%20willed%20away%20from%20them%20and%20daughters%20are%20not%20disinherited%20through%20Wills.%20This%20also%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20Code%20is%20not%20trying%20to%20either%20reform%20the%20law%20or%20make%20it%20gender%20just.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provisions%20regarding%20succession%20in%20the%20Code%20are%20also%20applicable%20to%20Hindus%20under%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%20and%20the%20Indian%20Succession%20Act%2C%20which%20addresses%20general%20laws%20relating%20to%20%E2%80%98wills%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20succession%20to%20the%20estates%20of%20Christians%20and%20Parsis.%20However%2C%20some%20beneficial%20provisions%20of%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%2C%20which%20restrict%20the%20right%20to%20will%20to%20only%20one-third%20of%20the%20property%20away%20from%20heirs%2C%20have%20not%20been%20recognised.%20The%20right%20to%20will%20all%20one%E2%80%99s%20property%20has%20been%20adopted%20from%20English%20Law.%20Nevertheless%2C%20some%20European%20and%20other%20countries%20have%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20the%20right%20to%20will%20to%20safeguard%20heirs.%20Women%20in%20India%20have%20been%20advocating%20for%20this%20right%20to%20prevent%20the%20property%20from%20being%20willed%20away%20from%20them%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20daughters%20are%20not%20disinherited%20through%20wills.%20This%20also%20underscores%20that%20the%20Code%20is%20not%20attempting%20to%20reform%20the%20law%20or%20make%20it%20gender-just.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20area%2C%20however%2C%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20proposed%20Code%20have%20been%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20section%2015%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%20(HSA)%2C%20if%20a%20female%20Hindu%20dies%20intestate%2C%20her%20self-acquired%20property%20unfairly%20devolves%20on%20the%20heirs%20of%20the%20husband%2C%20and%20only%20then%20upon%20her%20own%20mother%20and%20father%20if%20she%20has%20no%20children%20or%20a%20husband.%20A%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Flawschoolcolumn%2Fhindu-succession-act-for-female-intestates-221707%5C%22%3Ejudgment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20upholding%20the%20statutory%20law%2C%20commented%20on%20the%20discrimination%20against%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20own%20parents%2C%20who%20could%20inherit%20only%20if%20her%20father%20and%20mother-in-law%20were%20not%20alive.%20In%20one%20instance%2C%20a%20working%20woman%2C%20a%20childless%20widow%20who%20lived%20with%20her%20parents%2C%20died%2C%20and%20her%20property%20was%20given%20to%20her%20in-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2015%20of%20the%20HSA%20also%20unfairly%20stipulates%20that%20any%20property%20inherited%20by%20a%20woman%20from%20her%20father%20or%20mother%20will%20devolve%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20her%20sons%20or%20daughters%20or%20their%20children%2C%20upon%20the%20heirs%20of%20the%20father.%20Similarly%2C%20any%20property%20inherited%20by%20a%20woman%20from%20her%20husband%20or%20her%20in-laws%20would%20devolve%20upon%20the%20heirs%20of%20the%20husband%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20her%20children%20and%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20UCC%20aims%20to%20eliminate%20the%20different%20rules%20of%20succession%20for%20the%20estate%20of%20male%20and%20female%20heirs%2C%20making%20the%20law%20more%20equitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20far%20as%20agricultural%20land%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20UP%20Zamindari%20Abolition%20and%20Land%20Reforms%20Act%2C%201950%2C%20which%20extends%20to%20Uttarakhand%2C%20still%20unfairly%20states%20that%20the%20heirs%20of%20a%20Bhumidar%20or%20Asami%20in%20the%20first%20place%20will%20only%20include%20the%20widow%2C%20an%20unmarried%20daughter%20and%20male%20lineal%20descendants.%20A%20married%20daughter%20can%20only%20inherit%20if%20they%20and%20the%20Bhumidar%E2%80%99s%20parents%20are%20not%20alive.%20Though%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%20was%C2%A0%20amended%20in%202005%20to%20withdraw%20the%20exemption%20earlier%20given%20to%20the%20Land%20Reforms%20Act%20from%20the%20application%20of%20the%20HSA%2C%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20has%20not%20seen%20it%20fit%20to%20remove%20this%20discriminatory%20provision%20in%20its%20Land%20Reforms%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20procedure%20prescribed%20under%20section%20381%20of%20the%20proposed%20Bill%20mandates%20the%20compulsory%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20with%20the%20registrar.%20The%20registrar%20in%20the%20Code%20is%20vested%20with%20very%20wide%20powers%20to%20summon%20the%20parties%20for%20verification%20and%20ask%20for%20%E2%80%9Cnecessary%E2%80%9D%20additional%20information%20and%20evidence.%20One%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20misuse%20that%20this%20verification%20process%20can%20result%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provision%20is%20obviously%20unconstitutional%20and%20directly%20interferes%20with%20the%20rights%20of%20adult%20human%20beings%20to%20choose%20their%20partners%20and%20live%20with%20whomever%20they%20want%20without%20any%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20a%20draconian%20proviso%20to%20this%20section%20stipulates%20that%20registration%20can%20be%20denied%20if%20the%20live-in%20relationship%20is%20against%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20policy%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmorality.%E2%80%9D%20Thus%20the%20registrar%20can%2C%20by%20moral%20policing%2C%20refuse%20to%20register%20a%20live-in-relationship%20if%20it%20is%20against%20patriarchal%20norms%20which%20he%20espouses%20and%20bring%20a%20halt%20to%20inter-caste%20and%20inter-faith%20and%20other%20relationships.%20Furthermore%2C%20it%20will%20be%20obligatory%20for%20the%20partners%20of%20the%20live-in%20relationship%20within%20the%20state%20and%20absurdly%20outside%20the%20state%20(if%20one%20of%20them%20is%20an%20Uttarakhandi)%20to%20register.%20The%20non-registration%20within%20the%20month%20of%20the%20relationship%20will%20result%20in%20a%20punishable%20offence%20for%20a%20term%20of%20imprisonment%2C%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20provisions%20make%20it%20impossible%20for%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20to%20exist.%20The%20act%20of%20registration%20of%20a%20live-in-relationship%20is%2C%20thus%2C%20not%20an%20act%20which%20recognises%20live-in-relationships%20but%20an%20act%20which%20seeks%20to%20regulate%20how%20and%20with%20whom%20these%20relationships%20can%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20proposed%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%20does%20not%20promote%20either%20gender%20justice%20or%20substantive%20equality%20for%20women%20or%20further%20the%20cause%20for%20a%20just%20and%20equal%20family%20code%20for%20all%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021st%20Law%20Commission%20had%20said%20that%20the%20UCC%20was%20neither%20necessary%20nor%20desirable%20and%20the%20personal%20laws%20of%20each%20community%20could%20easily%20be%20reformed%20separately%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20affected%20members%20of%20that%20community.%20It%20has%20further%20remarked%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20countries%20are%20now%20moving%20towards%20recognition%20of%20difference%2C%20and%20the%20mere%20existence%20of%20difference%20does%20not%20imply%20discrimination%2C%20but%20is%20indicative%20of%20robust%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKirti%20Singh%20is%20a%20lawyer%20and%20an%20activist.%20She%20is%20a%20former%20member%20(part-time)%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20and%20a%20legal%20advisor%20in%20AIDWA.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707820236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111222%2Fimage-1824.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-the-uniform-civil-code-falls-short-in-advancing-gender-justice%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Critics%20argue%20that%20while%20the%20UCC%20aims%20to%20standardise%20laws%20across%20different%20communities%2C%20it%20fails%20to%20address%20key%20issues%20such%20as%20women's%20rights%20to%20marital%20property%2C%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20and%20inheritance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-the-uniform-civil-code-falls-short-in-advancing-gender-justice%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mobile%20internet%20suspended%20in%20Senegal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707820093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107660325%2Cimgsize-91920.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmobile-internet-suspended-in-senegal%2Farticleshow%2F107659643.cms%22%2C%22summa