%20using%20Indian%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20adds%20that%20he%20used%20a%20native%20variety%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20chair%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20and%20cheap.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20point%20in%20making%20a%20product%20that%20the%20masses%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford.%20It%20defeats%20the%20entire%20sustainability%20angle%20behind%20the%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CGujarat%20government%20has%20also%20released%20a%20lot%20of%20schemes%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20grow%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20funding%20the%20project%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20it%20out%20of%20my%20own%20pocket.%20I%20knew%20if%20I%20had%20gone%20out%20looking%20for%20funding%20then%20this%20would%20not%20have%20happened.%20Investors%20would%20lack%20confidence%20in%20the%20idea%20since%20it%20was%20new%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Ankit%20nearly%20two%20years%20to%20complete%20the%20design%20and%20make%20the%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20get%20the%20chair%20patented.%20The%20main%20reason%20behind%20it%20was%20to%20showcase%20the%20potential%20of%20native%20bamboo%20species%20to%20the%20world.%20Once%20my%20design%20got%20patented%2C%20it%20generated%20a%20conversation%20among%20people%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabc